    "description": "A unified platform to distinguish Klebsiella species K- and O-antigen types, model antigen structures and identify hypervirulent strains.\n\nKlebsiella species serotype predictor and surface antigens modeler.\n\nK-PAM (Klebsiella species serotype predictor and surface antigens modeler) is an in silico diagnostic tool that can predict the serotype of Klebsiella spp. (K- and O-types) using the gene protein sequences of proteins involved in biosynthesis and transportations of CPS and LPS.\n\nThe following documentation is to help the user in usage of K-PAM web server.",
